Responses back to client:
* HTTP mode: upstream status/body piped directly to HttpExchange response (zero-copy).
* RabbitMQ mode: return 202 Accepted once publish confirm succeeds (or 500 on failure).

Backpressure paths:
- Rate/semaphore limit → 429
- Channel pool timeout → release permit + 429
- Circuit breaker open → 503